# Netlify Nodescraper

----
## What is this?
A Node-based web-scraper hosted through Netlify's cloud-based functions. Serverless.

Made mostly for personal use for websites I frequent and always wished I could have API access for.

----
## Current Endpoints
-  http://localhost:9000/.netlify/functions/dboom-highlights
-  http://localhost:9000/.netlify/functions/dboom-mostrecent

